@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}

<h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

<section class="mt-4 mb-5">
    <h3>Health Data Protection & POPI Act Compliance</h3>
    <p>
        HealthCheck is committed to protecting your personal and health-related information in accordance with the South African Protection of Personal Information (POPI) Act and other applicable data protection laws. We ensure that all health data is handled with the highest standards of confidentiality, integrity, and security.
    </p>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Data Collection:</strong> Only necessary personal and health information is collected for the purpose of providing healthcare services and managing appointments.</li>
        <li><strong>Data Usage:</strong> Your data is used solely for healthcare management, appointment booking, and communication with healthcare professionals.</li>
        <li><strong>Data Storage:</strong> All data is securely stored using industry-standard encryption and access controls. Only authorized personnel have access to your information.</li>
        <li><strong>Data Sharing:</strong> We do not share your personal or health data with third parties except as required by law or with your explicit consent.</li>
        <li><strong>Data Retention:</strong> Personal and health data is retained only as long as necessary for the purposes described, or as required by law.</li>
        <li><strong>Your Rights:</strong> You have the right to access, correct, or request deletion of your personal information. You may also request information about how your data is processed.</li>
        <li><strong>Security Measures:</strong> We implement robust technical and organizational measures to protect your data against unauthorized access, loss, or misuse.</li>
        <li><strong>Children's Privacy:</strong> We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 18 without parental consent.</li>
        <li><strong>Contact:</strong> For privacy-related queries or requests, please contact our Data Protection Officer at <a href="mailto:privacy@healthcheck.co.za">privacy@healthcheck.co.za</a>.</li>
    </ul>
    <p>
        By using HealthCheck, you consent to the collection and processing of your personal and health information as described in this policy.
    </p>
</section>
